3419.Name: Connecticut States 2022
3419.Details:
Feb 16, 2022
32 Team draw (with a waitlist) $200 per team
Both players PTI must be 25+ or above on date of registration.
Registration closes on January 8th and we will take the lowest combined 32 PTI teams. There will be a waitlist until the date of the tournament and teams will be admitted off the waitlist based on combined PTI. 
Main draw matches: Best of 3 sets
Consolation matches: 2 out of 3 sets with 10 point tie-breaker in lieu of a 3rd set.
Lunch/Favor/Prizes
3419.RegistrationDetails:
All players must be current APTA members or pay a $30 Limited Membership Fee, good for one tournament.
We will keep all checks until the day of the tournament.  Players will be notified of acceptance into the tournament on January 9, 2022.
3419.Question1: What is sweatshirt size for you and your partner? - Must list 2 sizes.
